WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:17.400
Help!

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:18.680
Help!

00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:24.680
Let go of me!

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:27.960
They are Japanese. We can't interfere.

00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:29.360
If we swallow this anger,

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:30.760
are we still men?

00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:32.280
Let go of me!

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:37.000
Help!

00:01:37.240 --> 00:01:38.120
Bastards!

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:40.160
Bastards!

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:48.479
I am Japanese.

00:01:48.759 --> 00:01:49.890
You dare not kill me.

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:15.560
Brother,

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:17.079
we killed these two Japanese.

00:02:17.079 --> 00:02:18.940
How can we be police officers now?

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:21.420
This uniform is too dirty.

00:02:21.600 --> 00:02:22.860
I don't want it anyway.

00:02:24.920 --> 00:02:25.560
Miss.

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:32.320
You can't stay here anymore.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.280
Hurry and find a relative's house

00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:35.120
to hide.

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:37.650
I don't have any relatives,

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:39.920
or a home anymore.

00:02:41.600 --> 00:02:42.720
My parents

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:44.860
and my younger brother

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:47.960
were all killed by the Japanese.

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:50.840
I have nowhere to go.

00:03:31.720 --> 00:03:32.320
Jin,

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:33.920
here is the latest list.

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:40.960
You look very stylish today.

00:03:52.920 --> 00:03:55.040
I want to discuss something with you.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:57.240
What have you been busy with lately?

00:03:58.920 --> 00:03:59.840
I...

00:04:02.840 --> 00:04:03.520
Lingzi,

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:06.450
you are growing more and more distant from me.

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.900
Brother, what are you saying?

00:04:09.160 --> 00:04:11.120
I would never be distant from you.

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:12.600
Really?

00:04:15.960 --> 00:04:18.000
Brother, actually,

00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:21.680
I've always wanted to talk to you about something.

00:04:24.440 --> 00:04:25.770
If it's not convenient,

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:27.930
you don't have to say it now.

00:04:32.840 --> 00:04:33.480
Brother,

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:35.240
you know

00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:36.960
I hate the Japanese.

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:38.440
You hate them too.

00:04:40.440 --> 00:04:42.760
You saved me back then, took pity on me,

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:45.120
acknowledged me as your sister,

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:47.280
raised me, paid for my education,

00:04:47.520 --> 00:04:50.640
and sent me to be a teacher at Congde Girls' Primary School.

00:04:50.640 --> 00:04:53.000
With you and Second Brother protecting me these years,

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:55.800
my life has been more peaceful than anyone else's.

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:56.760
But brother,

00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:58.600
my heart tells me

00:04:59.159 --> 00:05:00.420
I have to do something.

00:05:02.440 --> 00:05:05.000
Some things are not for girls to do.

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:06.240
Brother,

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.120
if it weren't for you,

00:05:08.120 --> 00:05:10.250
I wouldn't have survived until today.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.960
Every day I live now

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:15.440
is a bonus.

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:18.540
Don't think nonsense.

00:05:19.480 --> 00:05:20.610
You are still young.

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:22.250
You have to live well for me.

00:05:29.880 --> 00:05:30.600
As for me,

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:32.240
I just hope

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:33.960
you and Chen Yu

00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:36.200
will get married as soon as possible.

00:05:36.200 --> 00:05:38.280
As long as you two can start a family

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:40.000
and live a peaceful life,

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.560
I haven't been your brother

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:44.520
in vain.

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.320
So you cannot take any risks.

00:05:46.440 --> 00:05:48.440
Who doesn't want to live a good life?

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:50.200
But the Japanese

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:52.560
want us to be slaves of a conquered nation.

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:54.720
Is that a life fit for human beings?

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:57.159
If we don't drive the Japanese

00:05:57.159 --> 00:05:59.159
out of Harbin, out of the Northeast,

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:00.320
and out of China,

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:02.080
my life would be in vain.

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:03.840
To drive the Japanese out,

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:06.240
can you manage it?

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:08.640
Brother,

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:10.280
please give that back to us.

00:06:10.400 --> 00:06:12.000
It's really important to us.

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:13.880
Brother!

00:06:15.560 --> 00:06:16.360
Brother!

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:25.480
The Electricity Bureau will precisely divide Xinshi Street,

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:26.440
dividing this area

00:06:26.440 --> 00:06:28.160
into 12 power supply zones.

00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:30.400
Every week, two of these zones

00:06:30.520 --> 00:06:32.760
will have scheduled power outages at night.

00:06:32.760 --> 00:06:33.420
In this way,

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:35.920
we can force the underground party's radio station

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:37.800
to use batteries to transmit messages.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:39.000
Section Six of the Security Bureau

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:41.640
has set up a PJ80 direction finder on the roof.

00:06:41.880 --> 00:06:43.640
Our fixed direction-finding station on the roof

00:06:43.640 --> 00:06:44.920
and our direction-finding vehicles

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:46.880
will form an air-ground coordination

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:47.760
to simultaneously capture

00:06:47.760 --> 00:06:49.080
the signal strength changes

00:06:49.080 --> 00:06:50.440
of the Communist underground radio station.

00:06:50.440 --> 00:06:53.280
Through algorithm calculation and triangulation,

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:55.880
we can reduce the current detection error of 500 meters

00:06:55.880 --> 00:06:57.720
to within 150 meters.

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:01.600
The Security Bureau's Wireless Counter-Espionage Team will carry

00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:03.060
mobile direction finders

00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:05.650
to check every floor and every household.

00:07:07.440 --> 00:07:08.760
Chief Qian, Deputy Chief Chen.

00:07:08.760 --> 00:07:09.480
Yes.

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:12.120
Once the detection area is locked,

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.640
the Special Service Section and the Action Team

00:07:13.640 --> 00:07:14.800
must take immediate action

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:15.800
to block the block

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:17.080
and make arrests.

00:07:17.080 --> 00:07:17.680
Yes, sir.

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:45.640
This tune

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:47.370
is from my hometown,

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:49.080
called 'Yueya Wugeng'.

00:07:49.880 --> 00:07:51.159
When I was young,

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:55.120
the night watchman in my hometown loved to listen to this.

00:07:56.120 --> 00:07:57.980
Listening to it on a winter night,

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:00.410
it sounds like a cat purring on a warm kang,

00:08:00.840 --> 00:08:04.120
and like firewood crackling in the snow.

00:08:05.320 --> 00:08:06.800
Sir, some say

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:08.040
the harmonica is too vulgar

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:10.040
and unsuitable for refined tastes.

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:12.760
Not at all.

00:08:14.520 --> 00:08:16.200
Those who say the harmonica is too vulgar

00:08:16.200 --> 00:08:17.880
don't understand music at all.

00:08:17.880 --> 00:08:19.320
In my opinion,

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.800
this small iron box

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:23.800
can not only hold

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:26.240
the waves of the entire Songhua River,

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:27.920
but also contain

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:31.540
the unbridled laughter of women in the sorghum fields.

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:35.120
Well said.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:41.260
This gentleman speaks extraordinarily

00:08:41.400 --> 00:08:42.720
with outstanding temperament.

00:08:42.720 --> 00:08:44.840
May I ask where you work?

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:46.320
I am Zhou Zhi.

00:08:46.800 --> 00:08:48.520
I work at the 'Binjiang Times'.

00:08:48.520 --> 00:08:49.580
'Binjiang Times'.

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:50.730
We read it every day.

00:08:53.400 --> 00:08:54.120
It seems

00:08:54.560 --> 00:08:56.690
the sales of our newspaper are not bad.

00:08:57.520 --> 00:08:59.240
There is an author named Yisuoyanyu

00:08:59.240 --> 00:09:00.720
who writes good serialized martial arts novels

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:03.760
in the literature section on the third page of the 'Binjiang Times'.

00:09:03.760 --> 00:09:04.720
Yisuoyanyu

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:06.320
is this Mr. Zhou Zhi.

00:09:12.920 --> 00:09:13.560
The Security Bureau

00:09:13.560 --> 00:09:14.840
has installed fixed direction finders

00:09:14.840 --> 00:09:15.680
on top of the Chinese Eastern Railway Administration building,

00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:17.000
which is right here.

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:19.280
The Secret Service action team is on standby.

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:20.560
Comrade Zhang Dajiang instructed

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:22.440
that in response to the enemy's air-ground coordinated deployment,

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:24.770
we must take technical countermeasures.

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:27.200
Heming,

00:09:27.400 --> 00:09:29.400
if we assemble a high-frequency transmitter,

00:09:29.400 --> 00:09:31.080
can we use specific signals

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:32.200
to interfere with the enemy's

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:35.200
direction-finding equipment signals and analysis?

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:36.440
Theoretically, yes.

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:38.160
The Type 91 receiver

00:09:38.400 --> 00:09:39.320
uses radio compass

00:09:39.320 --> 00:09:40.840
and interferometer direction-finding technology.

00:09:40.840 --> 00:09:42.640
The compass calculates direction

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:44.320
by comparing the intensity difference of signals

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:45.480
received by different antennas.

00:09:45.480 --> 00:09:47.080
The interferometer calculates angle

00:09:47.080 --> 00:09:48.760
by using the phase difference of signals

00:09:48.760 --> 00:09:49.920
received by multiple antennas.

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:52.080
If our radio

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:54.280
uses the 7.27 MHz band,

00:09:54.760 --> 00:09:55.760
and the transmitter

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:57.680
simultaneously transmits this frequency signal,

00:09:57.680 --> 00:09:58.360
it could cause

00:09:58.360 --> 00:09:59.840
their direction finders and direction-finding vehicles

00:09:59.840 --> 00:10:02.640
to experience multi-source signal misjudgment.

00:10:02.800 --> 00:10:03.960
The most important thing now

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:05.320
is to assemble the transmitters.

00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:05.920
Moreover,

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:06.960
one transmitter

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:08.560
is not enough to counter the Japanese's

00:10:08.560 --> 00:10:10.090
air-ground coordination.

00:10:12.680 --> 00:10:13.720
The core of the transmitter

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:15.980
is the vacuum tube oscillation circuit.

00:10:16.320 --> 00:10:18.760
It requires 6J1 and 6P1 model vacuum tubes.

00:10:24.760 --> 00:10:25.840
The Japanese now

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:28.080
treat all vacuum tubes, capacitors,

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:30.440
and other electrical components as military supplies,

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:33.320
strictly prohibiting private trading among civilians.

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:34.160
Where are we supposed to get

00:10:34.160 --> 00:10:36.160
these capacitors and vacuum tubes?

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:37.410
The black market

00:10:38.040 --> 00:10:39.570
is the only viable channel.

00:10:39.880 --> 00:10:40.760
Where is

00:10:41.320 --> 00:10:42.320
the black market?

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:43.800
The black markets in Harbin

00:10:43.800 --> 00:10:45.600
are concentrated in Baza Market

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:47.600
and around Qiulin on Xinshi Street.

00:10:47.920 --> 00:10:48.640
Heming,

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:50.160
write me a list,

00:10:50.280 --> 00:10:52.010
and I'll figure something out.

00:10:58.680 --> 00:10:59.320
Brother,

00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:00.360
this matter,

00:11:00.360 --> 00:11:02.220
you have to help us no matter what.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:04.760
Vacuum tubes,

00:11:05.240 --> 00:11:07.200
capacitors, resistors.

00:11:07.760 --> 00:11:09.240
This is quite a large amount.

00:11:09.240 --> 00:11:09.840
What for?

00:11:10.640 --> 00:11:12.900
Are you assembling a telegraph machine?

00:11:14.040 --> 00:11:14.680
No.

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:16.200
Then what is it for?

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:18.860
Without these things,

00:11:18.920 --> 00:11:20.320
we'll be in great danger.

00:11:21.160 --> 00:11:22.040
With these things,

00:11:22.040 --> 00:11:23.320
you'll be safe, right?

00:11:23.560 --> 00:11:26.160
With these things, you'll be in even more danger.

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:27.000
Everything on here

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:28.800
is Japanese controlled materials.

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:31.130
If the Japanese find out, heads will roll.

00:11:31.640 --> 00:11:33.760
Brother, please help us.

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:36.400
You must have a channel in the black market.

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:39.480
Who told you that?

00:11:41.840 --> 00:11:42.770
I'm telling you,

00:11:43.440 --> 00:11:45.320
stop hanging out with the people from the Harmonica Club,

00:11:45.320 --> 00:11:46.650
especially that Qin Na.

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:48.720
If something happens to you,

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:49.850
what will Chen Yu do?

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:52.160
If something happens to you,

00:11:52.160 --> 00:11:53.680
I won't have a good life for the rest of my days.

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:54.610
Do you know that?

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:57.120
Brother, I know you and Chen Yu are worried about me.

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:57.800
I didn't want to drag you into this.

00:11:57.800 --> 00:11:59.960
Why are you so disobedient?

00:12:00.080 --> 00:12:01.600
Brother, when have I ever disobeyed you?

00:12:01.600 --> 00:12:03.240
It's just this one thing that made you worried.

00:12:03.240 --> 00:12:04.400
We really have no choice.

00:12:04.400 --> 00:12:06.000
We really need these components urgently.

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:07.120
Please help us.

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:07.680
No.

00:12:08.200 --> 00:12:08.840
Brother.

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:12.000
Sister Qin asked me to give this to you.

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:13.240
She said if it's not enough,

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:14.880
we can add more.

00:12:24.040 --> 00:12:25.000
You tell Qin Na,

00:12:25.280 --> 00:12:26.280
tell her I said,

00:12:26.560 --> 00:12:27.360
Shen Yan

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:29.440
doesn't need her money.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:32.920
Brother.

00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:35.020
If you won't help, I'll go myself.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.280
Go if you have a death wish.

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:40.840
Brother.

00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:42.260
Then I'm really going.

00:13:08.760 --> 00:13:09.320
Boss,

00:13:09.760 --> 00:13:10.520
can I ask you something?

00:13:10.520 --> 00:13:11.240
What is it?

00:13:12.520 --> 00:13:13.680
Do you have vacuum tubes?

00:13:13.680 --> 00:13:14.160
What?

00:13:14.240 --> 00:13:15.040
Vacuum tubes.

00:13:15.520 --> 00:13:16.960
No, no, no. Go, go, go.

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:23.560
Boss.

00:13:24.280 --> 00:13:25.760
I want to ask you something.

00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:27.160
Do you sell vacuum tubes?

00:13:27.200 --> 00:13:27.880
What?

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:28.800
Vacuum tubes.

00:13:29.320 --> 00:13:29.920
No.

00:13:30.040 --> 00:13:30.960
No, no. Hurry up and leave.

00:13:30.960 --> 00:13:32.320
Boss, I can pay a high price.

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:33.250
Name your price.

00:13:33.280 --> 00:13:34.000
I really don't have any.

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:35.240
Go, go, go. Just go.

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:39.260
Why doesn't anyone have them?

00:13:42.400 --> 00:13:43.640
What was he buying from you just now?

00:13:43.640 --> 00:13:44.700
What vacuum tubes?

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:45.920
Stop.

00:13:48.640 --> 00:13:49.840
What were you buying?

00:13:50.920 --> 00:13:51.560
Speak.

00:13:51.920 --> 00:13:52.560
Speak.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:54.440
What were you buying? Speak.

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:56.960
I wasn't buying anything.

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.160
Not buying anything?

00:13:59.480 --> 00:14:00.240
Go after him.